{"tid":899364,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"【求救】有無人成日有d強迫性既思想，諗到個頭爆都停唔到","createTime":"2018-11-12T11:15:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T16:22:37.000Z","uid":89543,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc27fcc664316375b0ce079fe0ee7d885a6c45b9","tid":899364,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:15:08.000Z","msg":"講講我情況先<br />\n本身玩樂器既（專業、要表演），日常做緊野既時候會忍唔住回想份譜有咩音。<br />\n好多時呢d都係靠muscle memory，憑空諗通常會漏。一諗唔到個人就會好緊張。一定要即刻摷份譜出黎睇。<br />\n有時明明係記到既，但又忍唔住不停咁諗去confirm佢，諗到個頭覺得要爆都停唔到落黎。不停咁諗之下個腦就愈累，愈累就愈不停咁諗，無限loop<br />\n有無人有類似呢d強迫症既情況，有咩辦法改善，個頭真係好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598bfd0731d3764b168a04a82d7929022d7d9038","tid":899364,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:17:36.000Z","msg":"我 輕度焦慮症"},{"pid":"005130233f96f552a153a37d1bff77e658c25c98","tid":899364,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"598bfd0731d3764b168a04a82d7929022d7d9038","tid":899364,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:17:36.000Z","msg":"我 輕度焦慮症"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:18:21.000Z","msg":"我可能都有d，但無睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5262dea8ce6f4ca1aea8b73a024b5c3803802c4c","tid":899364,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"005130233f96f552a153a37d1bff77e658c25c98","tid":899364,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"598bfd0731d3764b168a04a82d7929022d7d9038","tid":899364,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:17:36.000Z","msg":"我 輕度焦慮症"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:18:21.000Z","msg":"我可能都有d，但無睇醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"我都無 唯一放鬆嘅地方係gym房"},{"pid":"2534e1ddda1ec54cc8f3315441e544dbc9036436","tid":899364,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy